Savii, Inc.: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 28, 2017 2:04 PM ET
Health Care Technology

Company Overview of Savii, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Savii, Inc. develops home care software solutions for private duty home care agencies. The company offers Savii Care, a Web and mobile platform that simplifies and streamlines home care agencies’ workflow from referrals to billing and payroll. It also offers Savii Connect, an app to Savii Care that allows caregivers to manage schedules, document task completion, and access electronic care journals. The company was formerly known as Akili Software, Inc. Savii, Inc. was founded in 2014 and is based in Raleigh, North Carolina.


310 South Harrington StreetRaleigh, NC 27601United StatesFounded in 2014



Phone: 919-659-0350

www.saviicare.com







