About Us

See why home care agencies that switch to Savii Care's mobile-first platform spend 75% less time on scheduling, billing, and payroll tasks.
Savii Care's home care agency management platform is the most complete care coordination software available.  Automate your workflow from first referral through client billing with Savii Care.


Our Ideal Customer

Companies that provide in home care services to older adults and individuals with disabilities. 
These companies want to increase efficiency and adopt mobile first technology to help them compete in the digital age.
Accepts Private pay, Medicaid/Waiver, LTC Insurance.





